{"tid":656521,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門 友愛邨 鬼故《秋天不回來》","createTime":"2018-05-07T10:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T03:16:12.000Z","uid":142116,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"865223d7026b069a568a1e0101bdb05030b08369","tid":656521,"uid":142116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的～<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n好多人都知友愛邨係屯門猛鬼既地方之一，因為經常有人係友愛邨跳樓，而最出名跳樓事件就係紅衣女鬼。但我今日講既故事唔係紅衣女鬼，而係秋天不回來既故事。話說十五年前既今日，小弟我仲係三歲小朋友咩都唔識，呢個故事都係聽我阿哥講。當年我隔離住咗一家三口，爸爸媽媽仲有粒仔，住係愛X樓17樓，個仔個陣好似已經十八歲。<br />\n<br />\n秋天既某一日，佢帶咗一個叫阿妍既女仔返屋企，佢父母睇得出佢好鍾意呢個女仔，所以無反對佢地一齊。但好竟不常，突然個女仔無啦啦消失左咁，電話唔通，短訊唔覆，個男仔梗係好傷心，仲特登上個女仔屋企搵佢，發現個女仔已經搬走。第二年既秋天，男仔透過朋友既朋友口中得知，個女仔已經識到第二男仔仲計劃結婚。就係當日既凌晨時份，個男仔上左去十八樓後樓梯，係防煙門寫咗d野就跳左落街。<br />\n<br />\n後來每日凌晨時份，隔離鄰舍就會聽到好淒怨既男聲講：秋天不回來.......秋天不回來，又有用Marker寫野既聲。為左令事件平息，街坊們就係個男仔死忌又燒衣，又拜祭，希望令男仔安息。所以愛X樓十八樓既後樓梯被燒衣既煙熏到黑曬，至今對防煙門仍然存在。房屋處無諗過換左對門，同埋重新油過後樓梯既牆身同天花板。所以有時壞lift，我會搭到十六樓行返上去，唔會搭到十八樓行返落去，因為真係好乸恐怖，屌你老母～～～～<br />\n<br />\n附上圖片兩張<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><span style=\"color: green;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/182057_485919048464db0d4de152e2d41463b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F182057_485919048464db0d4de152e2d41463b0.png&h=85d3f197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/182058_b4ad05cc514a6252274ed91079c87e83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F182058_b4ad05cc514a6252274ed91079c87e83.png&h=1f427cc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c37566150095a0286192ac026b2c5e60ea2b6ce","tid":656521,"uid":116293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"more <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3b0d1dd4a26586d7e4ffbc780f3b0881233597","tid":656521,"uid":39352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"真唔撚真阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe71f1b4a9f0d2fe59b9e9d8614849070fea827a","tid":656521,"uid":142116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c37566150095a0286192ac026b2c5e60ea2b6ce","tid":656521,"uid":116293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"more <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"後來對父母搬走左 新鄰居搬入<br />\n隔離鄰舍好少人知道呢件事 <br />\n要住返咁上下長時間先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c90977cb16bfd1c7c344141459b552021270fc","tid":656521,"uid":142116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d3b0d1dd4a26586d7e4ffbc780f3b0881233597","tid":656521,"uid":39352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"真唔撚真阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"我都係聽人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對防煙門同熏黑既後樓梯的確存在"},{"pid":"759ba3c5dc9c775f635a80440bffb6242aed8b0c","tid":656521,"uid":116293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"但係點解過左咁多年啲字都咁清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d769358a14c7659daf183e3cd9da64a88235bdc","tid":656521,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09580be2b0b81a2aa49dfae46387dfcb00e7390e","tid":656521,"uid":142116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s